$Id: README 2179 2018-11-2 17:01:51 dczanella $

@page CorbaDpShutdown Test README File

  Objective: This test check start/stop OpenDDS infrastructure using a CORBA 
  During start() procedure it configures OpenDDS in RTPS Mode create a participant
  During stop() procedure it destroys a participant and shutdown
  Doing this at first time it is OK, but a second time it gets a SIG FAULT

Please refrain from "improving", extending or expanding this
test, if you need to change

  To run the test use the run_test.pl script:

$ ./run_test.pl

  the script returns 0 if the test was successful.

*/
